# Package: `@excalidraw/common`

## Role

- Foundation layer: **pure helpers**, shared constants, i18n keys, color utilities, throttling helpers, and browser-oriented utilities used across the monorepo.
- **No React** — keep this package framework-agnostic.

## Dependencies

- MAY depend only on what `packages/common/package.json` already allows (e.g. `tinycolor2`).
- MUST NOT import from `@excalidraw/math`, `@excalidraw/element`, `@excalidraw/excalidraw`, or `@excalidraw/utils` (avoid upward/cyclic coupling).

## Conventions

- Prefer small, well-named exports from `src/` and re-export via the package entry (`src/index.ts`).
- Colocate tests under `packages/common/tests/` or next to modules per existing patterns (`*.test.ts` / `*.test.tsx`).

## How to verify

- `yarn --cwd ./packages/common build:esm` (or `yarn build:common` from repo root) when exports or build output matter.
- `yarn test:app --watch=false` with a path filter on `packages/common` when tests exist for the change.
- Wide API surface changes: `yarn test:typecheck` and a broader test run (many packages depend on `common`).
